### Mock Employee Server (port 8112) - Direct API Testing
### These requests go directly to the stubbed server your API calls

### Get all employees
GET http://localhost:8112/api/v1/employee
Accept: application/json

###

### Get employee by ID (replace with valid UUID from list above)
GET http://localhost:8112/api/v1/employee/123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000
Accept: application/json

###

### Create new employee
POST http://localhost:8112/api/v1/employee
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Employee",
  "salary": 75000,
  "age": 30,
  "title": "Software Engineer"
}

###

### Delete employee (requires name in body, not ID in path)
DELETE http://localhost:8112/api/v1/employee
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Employee"
}

###

### Test rate limiting (run multiple times quickly)
